title: Ep 42 - People Are Either Vacuums or Chargers
itunes:title: Ep 42 - People Are Either Vacuums or Chargers
description:
Some people are vacuums - they suck the energy out of you and spending time with them will wear you out. Other people are chargers - spending time with them fills you with energy and new outlooks in life. In this episode we talk about your Top 5 and why you want to fill it with the "Chargers"
